}} Also [http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.02.0137%3Abook%3D8%3Achapter%3D30 Book 8, Chapter 30], and [http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.02.0137%3Abook%3D11%3Achapter%3D106 Book 11, Chapter 106].&lt;/ref&gt; In ''On the Nature of Animals'' (''Περὶ Ζῴων Ἰδιότητος'', ''De natura animalium''), [[Claudius Aelianus|Aelian]], quoting Ctesias, adds that India produces also a one-horned horse (iii. 41; iv. 52),&lt;ref&gt;{{cite book
